metadata.name: Qitty Qat #1
metadata.description:
Born and bred on the mean streets of the city, Qitty Qats rule the world after dark. One of them might appear in your window at 3:00 AM, bringing good dreams... or nightmares.
There are 200+ traits that 5,555 randomly generated Qitty Qats are made up of from the illustrations of SHAG.
